{"type": "article", "id": 49963, "title": "Lululemon CEO离职，以及，潮流品牌Bristol-Studio的2018秋冬系列挺好看 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-02-06T04:19:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4999, "name": "三宅一生"}, {"id": 905, "name": "Dover Street Market"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 1530, "name": "Lanvin"}, {"id": 45428, "name": "Lululemon"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180206120322Wrij7xZhdVv0tOc4.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Is-Lanvin-looking-for-a-buyer-to-take-on-a-majority-stake-,944347.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>传：Lanvin 寻求出售</strong></a> | 根据 wwd 引用的信息来源，Lanvin 目前正在与多家投资者进行谈判，打算出售公司的多数股权。据称，创意总监 Olivier Lapidus 上任后的首秀 2018 春夏系列并未能使潜在买家感到满意，另外，尽管控制着 Lanvin 75% 股权的台湾富翁王效兰一直拒绝放弃 Lanvin，但 Lanvin 迟迟不能找到解决业绩差的方案，这也可能使她改变主意。</p><p><a href=\"http://fortune.com/2018/02/05/lululemon-ceo-2/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Lululemon 总裁离职，因行为达不到公司标准</strong></a> | 日前，Lululemon 在一份声明中表示，首席执行官 Laurent Potdevin 宣布辞职，因为行为达不到公司及员工的期望，Potdevin 在四年前加入公司。Lululemon 将向他支付 335 万美元的预付工资以及 18 个月内另外支付 165 万美元的遣散费。目前，该公司正在积极寻找接班人选。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>2 月 10 日，PUMA 与英国视觉艺术家 <a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/article/2018-02-05/pumashantell-martin/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shantell Martin </a>合作款发布在即。 </p><p>来看看 lookbook，Shantell 的意识流线条非常生动有趣。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115831kLmUCxbSREFaZQ1r.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115830YxM8eLJnX0tNmRpf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115829TUIx1i3gDFPlrupj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115830dIxX49MmQUtiPwCu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115830ialR3K8dP4IGrNDw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115829FBzbtiQkHjoZ1Au2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802061158318hUGWPdbHrLnxy3T.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115831OGkTsyPnlmrhxLQ4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802061158318tAjFU6kDGKsrix1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115832lDoda9X0LGJtkZVv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115834nCExyhi7BNd5cYOZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115828XR1YS4JPeBDmAI3H.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115836YtIxGabLEJsF9Cmc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115836NCURQ21rgWwzoHkh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115836kn9vfMGSjaCKBwiF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115836AHu2UBCfqp1bPnvm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115836xfjQLqhirCRMDs3B.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802061158369CDV2kioa4Qrncvh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115843u3STCQowZqXaU2dH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/550703\" rel=\"nofollow\">三宅一生和 United Nude 推出 2018 春夏合作系列。</a></p><p>该系列包括黑白二色的超轻量休闲鞋，售价 37000 日元，还有加入了运动鞋细节的建筑感高跟鞋，共有四种颜色，售价 53000 日元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115919jl1hwYbKg2GtnxfH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667273\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115919YhtEig0G7HACzT6P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667273\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115921LIv35qoe1ECmTSzs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115921iJr4TvLHudlSxB68.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115921vuXZECMGVeJUTInb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115921f7NrRvEXUQ4qgVWA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115921bH2ezjhvIFJfO9W8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115922RtGiWEeA8NPQgIxH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115923yTtgq3RrHzNXALwB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115923h95QP17CJVLAIEqM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206115923iejwzlLrkyZFq8hu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>继伦敦、纽约、东京、新加坡之后，<a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/550583\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dover Street Market </a>的全球第五家门店选在了北京。 </p><p>这家店位于原北京三里屯太古里 I.T ，现更名为 Dover Street Market Beijing，它由 I.T 集团运营，Dover Street Market 负责规划和创意，售卖COMME DES GARCONS、Gosha Rubchinskiy、VETEMENTS 等多个品牌单品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206120037on4VeDfFhkawUHQj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.077273\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206120041HgnOLetsDjfYz3m9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>洛杉矶潮流生活方式品牌<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/bristol-studio-fw18/#slide-4\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Bristol-Studio 的 2018 秋冬系列</a>新品不错。<br></p><p>品牌创始人、设计总监 Luke Tadashi 称，该系列的灵感来自二战时期的日本社会，还有一部分单品是与 adidas 的特别合作款，包括黑白二色的 Crazy BYW 球鞋，还挺好看的。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206120025NdmYQaE9KBUDo61j.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.401051\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206120026dm0iJWYxyca3sA1B.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.401051\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206120027J8yzg1Uu9FlVYq6e.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.401051\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206120027lQ8IvchEOuopBLkz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.401051\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206120027NmET8a3i4pZQf5lh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.401051\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802061200284f3g2nRYVy8BbJHp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.401051\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802061200285ILoC9G64FJBs87g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.401051\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206120028Li2YJerq3p7Nc0VP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.401051\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802061200285FtrMokEGifpPwC6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.401051\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206120031rnIP7VUcZLbEd4ql.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802061200316WV5NO1Sh8sundUA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>还记得 Pharrell 和 adidas 色彩丰富的 Trail Holi 联名系列吗？ </p><p>最近，双方联手又发布了一双极富春日气息的鞋子<a href=\"https://hypebae.com/2018/2/pharrell-adidas-hu-nmd-trail-pink-glow-release-date\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Pink Glow</a>，它将于 3 月 2 日上架。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206120100mbiwBoSkyYehqX6n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206120115AktexLfKgo20ZaSP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：PUMA</p>"}